Michael John `` Mike '' Myers -LRB- born May 25 , 1963 -RRB- is a Canadian-born actor , comedian , screenwriter , and film producer , who also holds UK and US citizenship .
He is known for his run as a featured performer on Saturday Night Live from 1989 to 1995 , and for playing the title roles in the Wayne 's World , Austin Powers , and Shrek films .
He also directed the documentary film Supermensch : The Legend of Shep Gordon , and had a small role in Quentin Tarantino 's Inglourious Basterds in 2009 .